
Este directorio contiene un micro 'framework' con clases para definir y ejecutar 'unit tests',
al igual que una aplicacion, 'lpmaketest.py' que genera codigo C++ para una bateria de tests 
a partir de una plantilla (de extension .unit)

-- 

This directory contains a micro framework with classes for defining and executing unit tests,
as well as an application, 'lpmaketest.py', which generates C++ code for a test suite from a 
template (with extension .unit)

